    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i honestly dont know how much longer i can do this. seeing my kids struggle to take care of me, looking at how much money and stress it's costing them... it just feels like i'm a weight around their necks. i've lived a full life, i really have, but now i'm just a burden.",
