    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just about the money or the time. it's the way they look at me. and my health... it's going downhill so fast. i feel like i'm just waiting for something bad to happen anyway, and it's exhausting for everyone involved. i just wish i could go quietly while i still have some dignity left, instead of being a total nuisance for years to come.",
