    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know they love me, that's what makes it worse. i see them tired, i see them stressed... it feels selfish to keep going just because i'm afraid to die. and i'm thinking, if i could just... step aside, wouldn't that be a more selfless thing to do for them? to save them from all this? it almost feels like the kindest option.",
